dct_title_s: Lock Canal Project, map showing line of proposed lock canal with summit elevation at 85 feet : [Panama Canal].
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, bathymetric lines, and hachures. Oriented with north toward the upper left. In upper right margin: Plate VIII. Stamped over publisher: Isthmian Canal Commission. Bound with: Sea Level Canal Project, [maps of proposed sea level canal]; and, Lock Canal Project, profile of proposed lock canal with summit elevation at 85 feet.
dct_creator_sm: Canal Zone. Board of Consulting Engineers
dct_publisher_sm: [Balboa Heights, Canal Zone?] : Board of Consulting Engineers, Panama Canal, 1905.
